content: The Photography Museum is a very artistic photography exhibition, it is worth seeing, because the entire museum is very clever, exquisite and unique in the control of the light and shadow on the lines, it is very suitable for taking pictures and later conception of the painting, beautiful!
There is a Korean American Photo Art Museum in 20 windows of the Korean American Pharmaceutical Building~~ Pleasant and good
Very nice place, you can go see it again

In addition to exhibitions of Masters'works, the Photography Museum regularly offers courses on photography and related subjects. There is a small restaurant in the basement where you can meet some masters occasionally. The photographs displayed everywhere in the exhibition hall may come from a master, and you can't see any difference.
Feeling in a circle, suddenly the ideological realm improved a lot.
The venue is quite small. There are some photographic Masters'works, and there are some minority ones.
The area of the Photography Museum is very large. The photographic works here have won the Korean Photography Award. Most of the exhibitions are taken of natural scenery.
I like to see these photographs very much. Although I am not a photographer, it does not affect my appreciation of these good works at all.
